description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30 MIN YOGA WORKOUT || Heart Opening Feel Good Flow' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Light.

Original workout description: Open your heart and maintain a healthy spine with this 30 Minute Yoga Workout Flow. Not only will you stretch and flow through heart opening sequences but you will work the core to keep your body strong and flexible!
